name: **Inishcannon**
description: Inishcannon L900-928 Sheet 30 An unpleasant ungrazed lump in 2006, grazed by sheep in 2012, and though formerly severely rat infested, the rats have departed. It has the remnants of a recent shack and a septic tank/well/holding tank, with a dangerously flimsy fibre glass top.
